race.comment: COMPADRE (3) improving gelding who indicated a win was imminent when fourth at his second race start over 1300m at Gunnedah. Gets a similar set-up for this and looking for the mile now.  RUFUS ATTICUS (5) at his top for this and doesn't have to improve much to get off the mark. Gritty effort with the 59kg from back in the field to run second over 1300m at Gunnedah. In leading yard and trained on the track. QUESTIONABLE (4) best performance in three career starts when second over 1750m at Muswellbrook. Finds a suitable race with the blinkers being added. Genuine top-three player. VINO RAPIDO (13) is a five-start maiden who is well and truly overdue. Sharp improver second-up when third over 1300m at Dubbo. Claim helps and sure to be thereabouts.
